  "decision_conditions": [
    "REASON: The proposed mansard roof extension and associated increase in height of boundary parapet/chimney, would be situated within a terrace that has a uniform and unaltered roofline, and by reason of its size, form, and location, would be an overdominant and incongruous element within the terrace, disrupting the rhythm and unity of an unbroken roofline. The development is therefore contrary to policies D4 (Designing in Context) and D11 (Alterations and Extensions) of Islington Council's Unitary Development Plan (2002), Islington's Urban Design Guide (2006) and policy CS9 of Islington's Core Strategy 2011."
